<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #5cb85c; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
        .content { padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #5cb85c; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; margin: 15px 0; }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #777; text-align: center; }
        .details { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 15px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Book Successfully Issued</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>
        
        <p>Your request for <strong>{{bookTitle}}</strong> has been approved, and the book has been issued to you.</p>
        
        <div class="details">
            <p><strong>Book Title:</strong> {{bookTitle}}</p>
            <p><strong>Author:</strong> {{bookAuthor}}</p>
            <p><strong>Issue Date:</strong> {{issueDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>Due Date:</strong> {{dueDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>Renewals Remaining:</strong> {{renewalsRemaining}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Please return the book by the due date to avoid any late fees. You can renew the book from your account if needed.</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 25px 0;">
            <a href="{{myBooksLink}}" class="button">View My Books</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>.</p>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>Â© {{currentYear}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
